sources.description:
A Christmas Princess - Jessica is a struggling chef living in a trendy New York borough. Prince Jack, who's in the city for his family's annual Christmas charity dinner, finds himself in need of a last-minute chef for a royal event when he meets Jessica.
2019.  Stars: Shein Mompremier, Travis Burns, Erin Gray
